     H            Y.
     F** ABAR01 ************************************************
     F*  ..PRODUCT DEMAND FORECAST ACCUMULATION DATA CREATE..  *
     F*      I-HASADA                             97.0702      *
     F*      H-AMANO                              02.1223      *
     F* TCHK1 04/02/09 CHG UDAY ---> TIME:DD                   *
     F* ------------------------------------------------------------------------
     F* FUNCTION: IF TODAY'S DAY >= 20, THEN CHANGE YYYY/MM TO NEXT MONTH
     F* EX. FORECAST DATE = 2024/10, IF TODAY=2024/10/10 --> NO CAHNGE
     F* EX. FORECAST DATE = 2024/10, IF TODAY=2024/10/20 --> CAHNGE  TO 2024/11
     F**************************************************************************
     I            DS
     I                                        1   60WYM
     I                                        1   40WYY
     I                                        5   60WMM
TCHK1I* SYSTEM TIME
TCHK1I            DS
TCHK1I                                        1  140WSDT
TCHK1I                                        1   20WSSHHH
TCHK1I                                        3   40WSSNNN
TCHK1I                                        5   60WSSSSS
TCHK1I                                        7  100WSSYYY
TCHK1I                                       11  120WSSMMM
TCHK1I                                       13  140WSSDDD
TCHK1I                                        1   40WSSTM4
TCHK1I                                        1   60WSSTM6
TCHK1I                                        7  140WSSDAT
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           PYM     6
     C                     MOVE PYM       WYM
      *
     C*****      UDAY      IFGE 23
TCHK1C*          UDAY      IFGE 20
TCHK1C                     TIME           WSDT
TCHK1C           WSSDDD    IFGE 20
     C           WMM       IFEQ 12
     C                     ADD  1         WYY
     C                     Z-ADD01        WMM
     C                     ELSE
     C                     ADD  1         WMM
     C                     END
      *
     C                     MOVE WYM       PYM
     C                     END
      *
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
